Hi,

Hoping someone can assist or point me in the right direction of resolution an issue im facing with embed forms:

When I add the following embed script to my clients site, its automatically adding in a iframe:

&lt;script charset="utf-8" type="text/javascript" src="<http://js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js|js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js>"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
 hbspt.forms.create({
   region: "na1",
   portalId: "8799016",
   formId: "c22e5b4b-a45b-4522-969c-7646c48b8f4d"
 });
&lt;/script&gt;

However, when I add another embed code, for another section of the site the embed form code excludes the iframe HTML:

&lt;script charset="utf-8" type="text/javascript" src="<http://js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js|js.hsforms.net/forms/embed/v2.js>"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
 hbspt.forms.create({
   region: "na1",
   portalId: "8799016",
   formId: "5be55822-7a82-4074-a773-da681ec706b3"
 });
&lt;/script&gt;

Any ideas on what may be causing this issue?
